{"tid":176183,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[同居]廁板掀起, 放下問題","createTime":"2017-03-28T04:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T14:51:23.000Z","uid":72687,"like":5,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1fc43df3435310927337145a1dc44e93571cd308","tid":176183,"uid":72687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:29:45.000Z","msg":"我老婆覺得: 坐廁正常狀態為廁板放下<br />\n因為男人大便, 女人大便同埋女人小便都係坐係到<br />\n如男人需要企係到小便, 請將廁板掀起, 小便完再放下<br />\n最理想係男人可以好似德國佬咁坐係到小便<br />\n<br />\n我覺得: 咁樣係極端女權主義<br />\n坐廁既廁板正常狀態應該係掀起既<br />\n大家能力範圍內既生活小節要達到互相尊重<br />\n即係為下一個廁所用家著想<br />\n如女人用完, 順手將廁板掀起<br />\n男人用完, 順手將廁板放下<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇?"},{"pid":"b1fd70076cb8d8b46caa3b3c48a0c0e513b15dbd","tid":176183,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:30:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47a41bb2f38770e2f0ab310ba9dbdfb372779d69","tid":176183,"uid":91326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:32:25.000Z","msg":"咁都要講一餐，你同你老婆相處都唔係幾好<br />\n最公平係成個都放低哂，姐係連蓋都放埋、咁咪兩個都要拎起囉，你做男人咪拎多塊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f37882e92df02619b8a66efe3fbd4ee181d2f4","tid":176183,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:32:54.000Z","msg":"好小事啫,睇咩需要囉,揭起定放低都係一個動作啫,唔駛下下問題複雜化掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a043eb018a2addc3e1927416abb7f6765866770","tid":176183,"uid":88812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:33:00.000Z","msg":"一人退一步，兩個都接受"},{"pid":"0d4299b73b9d6b7f494964f7e786c2e322fbae69","tid":176183,"uid":52923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:34:11.000Z","msg":"廁板如果長時間放下<br />\n沖廁時細菌